If you want to leave it as-is, add ${syntaxPluginInfo} to the 'plugins' section to enable parsing.`;
      } else {
        helpMessage +=
          `\n\nAdd ${syntaxPluginInfo} to the 'plugins' section of your Babel config ` +
          `to enable parsing.`;
